%% Flow C — Waiter starts dining session and opens payment
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor W as Waiter
    participant S as Staff Console
    participant API as Backend
    participant T as Token Service
    participant G as Guest devices

    W->>S: Select table (IDLE)
    S->>API: POST dining_session.start
    API-->>S: status=DINING
    Note over G: QR still shows menu only

    W->>S: Enter bill lines (manual/import)
    S->>API: POST bill lines
    API-->>S: bill_version=1

    W->>S: Tap Open payment
    S->>API: POST payment_session.open
    API->>T: Issue join token + 6-digit PIN
    T-->>API: expires_at +15min
    API-->>S: Show PIN + payment monitor
    API-->>G: Poll detects payment_open (no bill without token)

    alt Waiter refreshes token
        W->>S: Refresh PIN
        S->>API: POST token.rotate
        API->>T: Invalidate old token
    end

    alt Cancel before any payment
        W->>S: Cancel payment mode
        S->>API: POST payment_session.cancel
        API-->>S: status=DINING
    end
